data.title: WPKN Archives: (Place name Here) Cliff Furnald
data.text:
Thursday Morning, 7:00 to 9:55 AM eastern time

This program actually is nameless, but in the new age of WPKN, everything must be named - like the birds of the air and the fish in the sea. So, welcome to my whatever it's called this week.

See a program guide for the show every week at www.wpkn.org/cliff

Music from around the globe: roots, folk, jazz and the odd lot. Plus news, weather, traffic and whatever else comes along.

And please join me on Facebook.

Read more about the music I play (sometimes) at www.rootsworld.com

Thanks for listening,

Cliff Furnald
